
Note:
This is a program that can simulate the distributing process of NTU course selection system. By using this, you can estimate how many credits you'll get and thus organize your  choices better.

How to use it:
1. Log in NTU course selection system ( https://if177.aca.ntu.edu.tw/index.php ) and press "Homepage". After doing these, you should see the list of courses you chose on this page.
2. Check the source code of this page. (The ways to check source code depends on your searching engine. You can try to right click the page and find whether there is an option such as "View Page Source".)
3. Copy the whole source code, delete all contents in lesson.txt, then paste the source code into lesson.txt.
  (If nothing goes wrong, the first several lines of lesson.txt should be same as lesson_example.txt.)
4. Run pick.py. It will simulate the distributing process and tell you the results.
5. You can repeat 4. for multiple times for better prediction.

More:
1. This program do not support courses such as Chinese languages, English and foreign languages, foreign languages, and calculus.



說明：
這是一個可以模擬台大選課系統的程式。你可以用這個程式來預測你大約能夠選上幾學分，並藉此來調整你的選課志願序。

使用方法：
１：登入台大選課系統（網址為 https://if177.aca.ntu.edu.tw/index.php ），點「首頁」。這時候你應該會看到你選的課的列表。
２：檢視這個網頁的原始碼。（每個搜尋引擎檢視原始碼的方式不太一樣。可以試著按右鍵，找是否有類似「檢視網頁原始碼」的選項）
３：把整份原始碼複製下來，刪掉lesson.txt的所有內容，再把複製下來的原始碼貼到lesson.txt裡面。
    （理論上，你的原始碼的前幾行跟lesson_example.txt的前幾行應該會長一樣）
４：可以跑pick.py了。他會對選課進行模擬，並告訴你你的選課結果。
５：可以多跑幾次，這樣比較能夠更精準的預測。

附註：
１：這份程式不支援國文、英外文、微積分等課程。